   Recall Furnaces

   Furnaces Recalled:  Pose Significant Fire Safety Risk, The U.S.
   Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC) Announces Recall of Furnaces
   in California.   To view additional information click here.  For a list
   of specific brand names and model numbers, please refer to CPSC's web
   page at www.cpsc.gov/cpscpub/prerel/prhtml01/01189.html.
